                            Spent Fuel Treatment

   [e.jpg] Argonne conducts major research and development efforts in
   support of the elimination of the DOE-owned spent nuclear fuel
   inventory and the disposal of high-level wastes in the nation's
   geologic repository or interim storage facility.
     * Electrometallurgical Technology
     * Spent Nuclear Fuel Storage & Evaluation
     * Solids Characterization of Waste Forms

